column1: This file was created by CMPT_ME_BEME_OP_INV_RETS using the 201509 CRSP database.
It contains value- and equal-weighted returns for portfolios formed on ME and INV.
The portfolios are constructed at the end of June.  INV is the change
in total assets from the fiscal year ending in year t-2 to the fiscal year ending in t-1
Annual returns are from January to December.
Missing data are indicated by -99.99 or -999.
The break points include utilities and include financials.
The  portfolios  include utilities and include financials.
Sum of BE / Sum of ME
